Winning numbers drawn in ‘Georgia FIVE Midday’ game
ATLANTA (AP) _ The winning numbers in Wednesday afternoon’s drawing of the Georgia Lottery’s “Georgia FIVE Midday” game were:
2-1-5-4-9
(two, one, five, four, nine)
